# Memory MCP Server Settings
# Use this file to configure the Memory MCP server for Claude Desktop
#
# Format:
# SETTING_NAME=value
#
# Optional Settings:
# -----------------
# DOCKER_IMAGE - Docker image name and tag (default: mcp/memory:latest)
# RESTART_CLAUDE - Whether to restart Claude Desktop if it's running (true/false, default: true)
# MEMORY_DATA_PATH - Path to store memory data (default: .memory-data)
#
# Examples:
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/memory:custom
# RESTART_CLAUDE=false
# MEMORY_DATA_PATH=/path/to/memory/data
#
# Default settings (uncomment and modify as needed):
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/memory:latest
# RESTART_CLAUDE=true
# MEMORY_DATA_PATH=.memory-data
